steps.html_instructions: Head west on Okullar Cd. toward 1 Nolu Sk.
Kademci Sk. turns slightly right and becomes Görgün Sk.
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit

Turn right onto Fatih Cd./Samsun-Sinop Yolu
Continue to follow Samsun-Sinop Yolu
Take the exit toward Kastamonu Sinop Yolu/D785

Turn left onto Boyabat Sinop Yolu/D030
Continue to follow D030
Slight right to stay on İstanbul Samsun Yolu/D100/E80

Turn left onto Ankara Bolu Yolu/D750
Continue to follow D750

Exit onto Eskişehir Yolu/D200/E90 toward Polatlı/Eskişehir/İzmir
Continue to follow D200/E90
Take the ramp to Afyon Ankara Yolu/D260/E96

Continue onto Afyon Ankara Yolu/D260/E96
Continue to follow D260/E96

Take the ramp onto Afyon Çevre Yolu/D300/E96
Continue to follow D300/E96

At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Fatih Cd.
Destination will be on the left
